I didn’t expect Song

295
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:15,900
to hire such a young lawyer.

296
00:17:18,500 --> 00:17:19,340
Please, have a seat.

297
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:29,260
I was going

298
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:31,220
to let my lawyer talk to you directly,

299
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:33,540
but then I figured

300
00:17:34,180 --> 00:17:36,580
I'd better say a few words myself.

301
00:17:38,900 --> 00:17:39,740
I am not

302
00:17:40,380 --> 00:17:42,220
an unscrupulous capitalist.

303
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:44,300
Mr. Song

304
00:17:44,300 --> 00:17:45,900
is a veteran employee of ours.

305
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,860
What he's contributed to the company

306
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:50,420
I've kept them in my heart.

307
00:17:50,540 --> 00:17:51,620
During his hospitalization

308
00:17:51,620 --> 00:17:52,820
and surgery,

309
00:17:53,020 --> 00:17:53,940
you can check,

310
