314
00:18:07,740 --> 00:18:08,980
What I want to say is,

315
00:18:09,580 --> 00:18:10,980
during Mr. Song's employment,

316
00:18:11,170 --> 00:18:12,420
there were no personal grievances

317
00:18:12,540 --> 00:18:14,260
between us.

318
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:17,860
We fairly, reasonably, and lawfully terminated

319
00:18:17,860 --> 00:18:20,500
an employee who no longer brought any value to the company,

320
00:18:21,180 --> 00:18:23,540
and we gave him full compensation.

321
00:18:24,580 --> 00:18:26,140
And what did we get in return?

322
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:27,820
His betrayal

323
00:18:27,820 --> 00:18:28,940
and gross slander

324
00:18:28,980 --> 00:18:30,340
have put my company

325
00:18:30,340 --> 00:18:31,980
at great risk.

326
00:18:32,060 --> 00:18:33,180
I won't tolerate it,

327
00:18:33,180 --> 00:18:35,380
nor will I let this kind of thing happen.

328
00:18:36,380 --> 00:18:37,830
An incapable employee gets dismissed

329
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:39,460
and then retaliates against the company.

330
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:41,620
If I allow this precedent,

331
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:44,180
how will I answer to my employees in the future?

332
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:46,500
What I must do

333
00:18:46,500 --> 00:18:48,500
is to protect the company's interests,

334
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:51,420
and the interests of every employee in this company.

335
00:18:57,410 --> 00:18:58,250
Alright.

336
00:19:00,340 --> 00:19:01,620
I've said my piece.

337
00:19:02,340 --> 00:19:03,420
You two

