339
00:19:07,540 --> 00:19:08,380
Mr. Hu, wait.

340
00:19:12,580 --> 00:19:13,820
I hope you're prepared.

341
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:15,460
We do not accept a settlement.

342
00:19:23,260 --> 00:19:24,180
Nonsense.

343
00:19:24,320 --> 00:19:26,380
Song must have acted rashly.

344
00:19:26,740 --> 00:19:27,580
Today.

345
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:29,700
I'll go talk to him again today.

346
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:34,260
Mr. Zhou, Mr. Hu,

347
00:19:35,620 --> 00:19:36,460
Ms. Tian.

348
00:19:37,420 --> 00:19:38,900
