the compensation Mr. Hu is giving you.

358
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:29,380
You must accept it.

359
00:21:34,580 --> 00:21:35,580
Don't worry,

360
00:21:35,780 --> 00:21:37,780
I'll settle all your hospital bills.

361
00:21:37,940 --> 00:21:41,580
(Emergency Observation Room)

362
00:21:43,300 --> 00:21:44,140
Ms. Ho,

363
00:21:45,260 --> 00:21:47,700
