364
00:21:48,220 --> 00:21:49,340
What was he here for?

365
00:21:49,620 --> 00:21:50,460
Ms. Ning,

366
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:52,740
Let's just end this here.

367
00:21:53,620 --> 00:21:55,500
My family doesn't want to see you anymore.

368
00:21:55,510 --> 00:21:57,150
