00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:25,180
Zhu,

373
00:22:27,020 --> 00:22:27,860
Zhu!

374
00:22:35,180 --> 00:22:36,940
Didn't you say she wouldn't come here?

375
00:22:40,700 --> 00:22:41,820
She hasn't come before.

376
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:44,140
She doesn't come to check up on things.

377
00:22:44,260 --> 00:22:45,700
So why are you so nervous?

378
00:22:55,380 --> 00:22:57,500
It has nothing to do with checking up.

379
00:22:58,020 --> 00:23:00,290
Then what does it have to do with?

380
00:23:07,740 --> 00:23:09,020
I don't like surprises.

381
00:23:13,450 --> 00:23:14,760
If you're coming next time,

382
00:23:17,740 --> 00:23:18,820
let me know in advance.

383
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:33,820
It's going to rain.

384
00:23:35,700 --> 00:23:36,740
Let me drive you back.

385
00:23:38,300 --> 00:23:39,140
Okay.

386
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:13,460
Do you enjoy

387
00:25:14,180 --> 00:25:15,580
