398
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:55,540
Where's Zhu?

399
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:56,780
Zhu is my employee.

400
00:25:57,300 --> 00:26:00,500
I intentionally arranged for him to go to the service station.

401
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:02,220
I thought

402
00:26:02,620 --> 00:26:04,180
