413
00:26:27,820 --> 00:26:28,660
Second,

414
00:26:29,860 --> 00:26:32,180
I think, taking the child into account,

415
00:26:33,100 --> 00:26:34,180
it's right

416
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:37,460
to close this chapter for you.

417
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:44,960
Honey,

418
00:26:47,780 --> 00:26:49,620
the reason I didn't tell you earlier

419
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:51,310
was because I didn't want

420
00:26:51,430 --> 00:26:52,900
to put too much pressure on you

421
00:26:53,780 --> 00:26:54,620
or

422
00:26:54,660 --> 00:26:56,100
make you upset.

423
00:26:57,740 --> 00:26:58,580
Actually,

424
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:01,780
Niuniu's mom was also arranged by me.

425
00:27:02,220 --> 00:27:03,220
I admit,

426
00:27:03,620 --> 00:27:05,340
I've been a bit over-involved.

427
00:27:05,860 --> 00:27:06,700
But

428
00:27:07,580 --> 00:27:09,620
I just want you to be happy.

429
00:27:10,980 --> 00:27:11,820
Honey,

430
00:27:12,980 --> 00:27:14,980
You've suffered these past few days.

431
00:27:15,660 --> 00:27:17,620
