432
00:27:25,460 --> 00:27:26,820
Is there anything else?

433
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:35,500
What else do you want to know?

434
00:27:36,580 --> 00:27:37,780
Confession gets leniency.

435
00:27:43,660 --> 00:27:44,500
I confess.

436
00:27:45,820 --> 00:27:46,660
Honey,

437
00:27:48,420 --> 00:27:50,860
everything I do

438
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:53,340
is for you

439
00:27:54,540 --> 00:27:55,740
and for this family.

440
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:21,620
Everything I do

441
00:28:22,620 --> 00:28:23,860
is for you

442
00:28:25,220 --> 00:28:26,420
and for this family.

443
00:28:50,420 --> 00:28:51,260
Mom,

444
00:28:51,780 --> 00:28:52,620
have some water.

445
00:28:53,420 --> 00:28:54,500
Mr. Hu

446
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:56,180
really cares about your mother.

447
00:28:56,300 --> 00:28:58,940
He calls every day to check on her.

448
00:28:59,460 --> 00:29:01,300
I've never seen such a good son-in-law.

449
00:29:03,060 --> 00:29:03,940
Isn't that right?

450
00:29:03,940 --> 00:29:06,040
Since your mother fell last time,

451
00:29:06,380 --> 00:29:08,080
Mr. Hu has been constantly reminding us,

452
00:29:08,170 --> 00:29:10,620
saying we must make sure nothing happens to her again.

453
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:12,540
My son-in-law is a smart man.

454
00:29:12,540 --> 00:29:13,380
He knows

455
00:29:13,700 --> 00:29:16,300
that treating me well means treating my daughter well.

456
00:29:18,180 --> 00:29:19,500
As for my son-in-law,

457
00:29:19,700 --> 00:29:20,740
I would say

458
00:29:20,820 --> 00:29:21,860
he's pretty much perfect.

459
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:23,820
I can’t find any faults.

460
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:27,660
That's what I'm talking about.

461
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:37,140
Mr. Zhou,

462
00:29:40,700 --> 00:29:41,540
Mr. Zhou.

463
00:29:43,940 --> 00:29:46,500
The contract with Ms. Lan is brilliant.

464
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:48,900
You've brought the company tremendous profits.

465
00:29:50,300 --> 00:29:51,140
Great job!

466
00:29:53,620 --> 00:29:54,460
Cheng,

467
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:56,980
about Song,

468
00:29:57,620 --> 00:29:59,580
considering Yao Feng is preparing to go public,

469
00:30:00,340 --> 00:30:01,940
we should give him more compensation.

470
00:30:02,310 --> 00:30:03,900
It's better to settle this peacefully.

471
00:30:04,020 --> 00:30:05,340
He's already promised me

472
00:30:05,340 --> 00:30:06,940
