473
00:30:07,900 --> 00:30:10,340
He'll sign the settlement agreement and send it to me today.

474
00:30:16,020 --> 00:30:16,860
Mr. Zhou

475
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,100
I'll leave everything

476
00:30:18,100 --> 00:30:20,020
to you to handle.

477
00:30:22,150 --> 00:30:24,100
I knew you

478
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:25,020
was magnanimous

479
00:30:25,020 --> 00:30:26,100
and tolerant,

480
00:30:26,380 --> 00:30:28,060
with great composure.

481
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:30,980
What's been settled?

482
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:32,380
You heard me.

483
00:30:32,390 --> 00:30:33,250
It's been settled.

484
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:36,260
Mr. Song, given Mr. Hu Cheng's usual style and demeanor,

485
00:30:36,260 --> 00:30:38,820
I don't believe he'll give you a fair and satisfactory result.

486
00:30:38,860 --> 00:30:39,860
And such case,

487
00:30:39,860 --> 00:30:41,070
if he's not punished as he should be,

488
00:30:41,190 --> 00:30:42,060
will continue

489
00:30:42,070 --> 00:30:43,780
to happen at Yao Feng Technology.

490
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:45,260
Does Mr. Hu get something on you?

491
00:30:45,260 --> 00:30:46,860
If so, tell me everything.

492
00:30:46,860 --> 00:30:48,620
I'll make sure we win this lawsuit.

493
00:30:48,860 --> 00:30:50,420
You're absolutely right

494
00:30:50,430 --> 00:30:51,840
about fairness and justice.

495
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:54,400
I totally agree.

496
00:30:54,730 --> 00:30:57,100
But Yao Feng's standing in the industry

497
00:30:57,220 --> 00:30:59,400
