529
00:32:03,300 --> 00:32:04,540
Sorry, madam,

530
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:06,620
We'll cover all of Li's medical expenses.

531
00:32:06,620 --> 00:32:07,580
Money, money, money.

532
00:32:08,380 --> 00:32:10,220
