538
00:32:25,100 --> 00:32:26,380
- No, it's not.
- Cheers.

539
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:28,180
- Cheers.
- To a successful partnership.

540
00:32:28,180 --> 00:32:29,000
- To a happy collaboration.

541
00:32:29,030 --> 00:32:30,300
Thank you, Ms. Lan, for your trust.

