550
00:32:45,100 --> 00:32:46,780
- Ms. Lan.
- Zhou Wei, have more.

551
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:47,900
- Okay.
- Thank you.

552
00:32:50,780 --> 00:32:51,660
Ms. Lan.

553
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:53,060
- Help yourself.
- Okay.

554
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:54,860
Mr. Hu, I toast to you.

555
00:32:55,100 --> 00:32:57,300
I hope we have more opportunities to work together in the future.

556
00:32:57,420 --> 00:32:58,740
Yeah, yeah, more communication.

557
00:32:59,260 --> 00:33:00,100
Definitely.

